msgctxt "sn48.40:3.7"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati sato ca "
"sampajāno sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti ‘upekkhako "
"satimā sukhavihārī’ti tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when, with the fading away of rapture, a mendicant enters and remains "
"in the third absorption, where they meditate with equanimity, mindful and "
"aware, personally experiencing the bliss of which the noble ones declare, ‘"
"Equanimous and mindful, one meditates in bliss.’ "

msgctxt "sn48.40:3.8"
msgid "ettha cuppannaṃ sukhindriyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"That’s where the faculty of pleasure that’s arisen ceases without anything "
"left over."

msgctxt "sn48.40:3.9"
msgid ""
