msgctxt "sn48.40:5.6"
msgid "Kattha cuppannaṃ upekkhindriyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati?"
msgstr ""
"And where does that faculty of equanimity that’s arisen cease without "
"anything left over?"

msgctxt "sn48.40:5.7"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of neither "
"perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation of "
"perception and feeling. "

msgctxt "sn48.40:5.8"
msgid "ettha cuppannaṃ upekkhindriyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati."
